  m_text: "THANKS FOR PLAYING !!\n\ni hope you enjoyed this short demo of orbitalls,
    this has been my first game jam and it has been a busy but fun experience!\n\nthe
    final game will have more levels, more planets, and more out-of-this-world mechanics!
    \nif i can finish this game in time that is *_*\n\ni'd love any feedback or suggestions
    you may have, so feel free to give your thoughts!\n\n thanks again for playing.
    :)"
